@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http
@using Elektrodistribucija.Data.Models
@using Elektrodistribucija.Web.Helper
@{ 
    KorisnickiNalog korisnik = Context.GetLogiraniKorisnik();
   
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title> Elektrodistribucija</title>

    <environment include="Development">

    </environment>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
    <script src="~/lib/jquery/dist/jquery.js"></script>

    <script src="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.aspnetcdn.com/ajax/jquery.validate/1.16.0/jquery.validate.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.aspnetcdn.com/ajax/jquery.validation.unobtrusive/3.2.6/jquery.validate.unobtrusive.min.js"></script>
    @*<script src="/js/site.js"></script>*@
    <script src="~/jsFIT.js"></script>
</head>
<body>


    <nav class="navbar navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-header">
                <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse">
                    <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                </button>

            </div>
            <div class="navbar-collapse collapse">
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                    <li><a asp-area="AdministratorModul" asp-controller="AdministratorHome" asp-action="Index">Početna</a></li>
                    <li class="dropdown">
                        <a class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#">Korisnici <span class="caret"></span></a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a asp-area="AdministratorModul" asp-controller="Korisnici" asp-action="Dodaj">Dodaj korisnika</a></li>
                            <li><a asp-area="AdministratorModul" asp-controller="Korisnici" asp-action="Prikazi">Prikaži korisnike</a></li>


                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li class="dropdown">
                        <a class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#">Direkcije <span class="caret"></span></a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a asp-area="AdministratorModul" asp-controller="Direkcije" asp-action="Dodaj">Dodaj direkciju</a></li>
                            <li><a asp-area="AdministratorModul" asp-controller="Direkcije" asp-action="Prikazi">Prikazi direkcije</a></li>


                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li class="dropdown">
                        <a class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown" href="#">Odjeli <span class="caret"></span></a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a asp-area="AdministratorModul" asp-controller="Odjel" asp-action="Dodaj">Dodaj odjel</a></li>
                            <li><a asp-area="AdministratorModul" asp-controller="Odjel" asp-action="Prikazi">Prikazi odjele</a></li>


                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><a asp-area="" asp-controller="Sesije" asp-action="Index">Sesije</a></li>

                </ul>
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                    <li> <a>Dobro došli @korisnik.KorisnickoIme </a></li>
                    <li>

                        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Login" asp-action="Logout">
                            Odjava
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container body-content">
        @RenderBody()
        <hr />
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2017 - Elektrodistribucija</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    

    @RenderSection("Scripts", required: false)
</body>
</html>
